880
01:02:08,604 --> 01:02:11,398
Cowboy's just down the road
in the platoon area.

881
01:02:11,565 --> 01:02:15,235
- You mind if we tag along, sir?
- No problem. Welcome aboard.

882
01:02:15,402 --> 01:02:18,614
By the way, my name's Schinoski.
Walter J. Schinoski.

883
01:02:18,780 --> 01:02:21,033
My people call me Mr. Touchdown.

884
01:02:21,200 --> 01:02:22,701
I played ball for Notre Dame.

885
01:02:22,868 --> 01:02:24,161
- Notre Dame?
- Yeah.

886
01:02:24,328 --> 01:02:27,039
- All right.
- You here to make Cowboy famous?

887
01:02:27,206 --> 01:02:28,790
