the NVA executing a lot of gook civilians.

897
01:02:55,400 --> 01:02:56,819
That's affirmative.

898
01:02:56,985 --> 01:03:00,614
I saw some bodies about a half a klick
this side of Phu Cam Canal.

899
01:03:00,823 --> 01:03:02,991
