914
01:04:11,101 --> 01:04:14,897
Well, it seems the NVA came in
with a list of gook names.

915
01:04:15,063 --> 01:04:19,610
Government officials, policemen,
ARVlN officers, school teachers.

916
01:04:19,776 --> 01:04:21,778
They went around
to their houses real polite...

917
01:04:21,945 --> 01:04:25,282
