the next day for political reeducation.

918
01:04:25,782 --> 01:04:28,076
Everybody who turned up got shot.

919
01:04:28,243 --> 01:04:29,870
Some they buried alive.

920
01:04:30,120 --> 01:04:31,413
Ready.

921
01:04:32,998 --> 01:04:34,458
Colonel.

922
01:04:35,959 --> 01:04:38,670
